sm.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/6840/', '', 'Opium, Eluxadoline, Diphenoxylate, Difenoxin', 'Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Dexlansoprazole, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Rifabutin, Nizatidine, Esomeprazole, Vonoprazan', 1767369485);
